{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}
  Card Game
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
  <div class="report-container report-container-mob">
    <aside class="toc">
      <h1>Card <br />game</h1>
      <span style="font-size:100px;">&#127137;</span>
    </aside>
    <main>
      <h1>Welcome to the Card Game!</h1>
      <div>
        <p>
          Explore a simple card game where you can view a full deck, shuffle it, and draw cards one by one or multiple at a time. Perfect for learning how a classic deck works â€” try it out and see what you draw!
          <br />
          To learn more about the card game visit: <a href="https://sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fransk-engelsk_kortlek">French-English Card game</a>
          <br />
        </p>
        <hr>
        <hr>
        <h2>Class structure and UML diagram</h2>
        <h3>Classes:</h3>
        <br />
        <ol>
          <li>
            <b>Card:</b> A base class that represents a playing card with suit and value properties. It provides methods to retrieve these attributes.
          </li>
          <br />
          <li>
            <b>CardGraphic:</b> This class is a extention of Card class and adds a getGraphic() method that returns a Unicode symbol for each card.
          </li>
          <br />
          <li>
            <b>Deck:</b> This class containes a collection of Card objects. This class has the method to create, shuffle and draw card from the collection of cards in the game that is a total of 52 at the start excluding the jockers.
          </li>
          <br />
        </ol>
        <h3>Relationships between classes:</h3>
        <br />
        <ul>
          <li>
            <b>Inheritance:</b> The CardGraphic-class inherits from the Card-class using the 'extends' keyword in php.
          </li>
          <li>
            <b>Composition:</b> The Deck-class has many Card-objects. 
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />

        <h3>UML Diagram:</h3>
        <a href="{{ asset('img/car-gameUML.png') }}"><img class="centered;" src="{{ asset('img/car-gameUML.png') }}" alt="diagram for classes" /></a>
        <br />
        <br />
        <hr />
        <br>
        <h3>List of routes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Session storage route: <a href="{{ path('session_store') }}">Link to Session variables</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Sorted deck of cards route: <a href="{{ path('card_deck') }}">Deck of Cards</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Shuffled deck of cards route: <a href="{{ path('card_shuffle') }}">Shuffled Deck of Cards</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Draw a card from the deck route: <a href="{{ path('card_draw') }}">Draw a card</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Draw a given number of cards from the deck route: <a href="{{ path('card_draw_number', { num: 1 }) }}">Draw 'n' cards card</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
